data.description: Don't miss out on this practically perfect home located in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Lexington Plantation! This home boasts the open floor plan you've been dreaming of, with a main-level primary bedroom complete with an ensuite bathroom and spacious walk-in closet. Upstairs, you'll discover the remaining four bedrooms, along with a convenient double vanity bathroom. The formal dining area features a charming, coffered ceiling and seamlessly opens to the stunning island kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances and elegant granite countertops. Step outside to the large backyard, offering ample space for entertaining and enjoying outdoor gatherings. Don't wait to make this your new home—schedule a viewing today!
